trans-unit.source: A persistence provider throws this exception when it expects to find an instance key in the unassociated state, but finds the key in a different state.
trans-unit.target: 永久性提供程序期望找到处于非关联状态的实例键时，会引发此异常，但找到处于不同状态。

trans-unit.target: 初始化的实例<xref href="System.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstanceKeyCollisionException"></xref>类作为参数传递的错误消息。
